      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2422849-blood-clotting-drug-derived-from-pigs-can-now-be-made-synthetically/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
